  <data name="PrivacyPolicy" xml:space="preserve">
    <value>&lt;h6&gt;1. Information We Collect&lt;/h6&gt; &lt;p class="font-monospace"&gt;When you use external authentication, we may receive and store:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Your first and last name&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Email address&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Unique identifier provided by the authentication provider&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Basic profile information (as permitted by the provider)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;h6&gt;2. Use of Information&lt;/h6&gt; &lt;p class="font-monospace"&gt;We use this information to:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Provide and maintain the authentication service&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Control access to our internal systems&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Identify and authenticate users&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Improve the security of our services&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;h6&gt;3. Information Sharing&lt;/h6&gt; &lt;p class="font-monospace"&gt;We do not share your personal information with third parties except:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;When required by law&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;To protect our rights or property&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;In the event of a merger, acquisition, or asset sale&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;h6&gt;4. Data Security&lt;/h6&gt; &lt;p class="font-monospace"&gt;We implement technical and organizational measures to protect your personal data from unauthorized access or alteration.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;h6&gt;5. Data Retention&lt;/h6&gt; &lt;p class="font-monospace"&gt;We retain your information as long as it is necessary for the purposes described in this policy or as required by applicable law.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;h6&gt;6. Your Rights&lt;/h6&gt; &lt;p class="font-monospace"&gt;You have the right to:&lt;/p&gt; &lt;ul&gt; &lt;li&gt;Request access to your personal data&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Request correction of inaccurate data&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Request deletion of your personal data&lt;/li&gt; &lt;li&gt;Object to the processing of your data&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;  &lt;h6&gt;7. Changes to this Policy&lt;/h6&gt; &lt;p class="font-monospace"&gt;We may update this policy from time to time. Updated versions will be posted on this site.&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;h6&gt;8. Contact&lt;/h6&gt; &lt;p class="font-monospace"&gt;For questions about this policy, please contact our privacy team at: privacidad@suempresa.com&lt;/p&gt;  &lt;p class="text-muted mt-3"&gt;&lt;small&gt;Last updated: April 14, 2025&lt;/small&gt;&lt;/p&gt;</value>
